// Northwestern / central Pashto (central Ghilji area), following the
// dialect columns of Wikipedia Help:IPA/Pashto. Relative to the
// southwestern (Kandahari) base ps voice:
//   ښ [ʂ] → [ç]     ږ [ʐ] → [ʝ]
//   څ [t͡s] → [s]    ځ [d͡z] → [z]
// ژ stays [ʒ]. C and J^ are the palatal fricatives from the base1 table.
replace 00 S. C
replace 00 Z. J^
replace 00 ts s
replace 00 dz z
